    slug: 'grouper',
    description: 'Marine groupers are the apex personalities of reef aquariums. From the Miniatus to the rare Blue-Spotted Grouper, these intelligent predators make commanding centrepiece fish.',
    metaTitle: 'Grouper Fish for Sale | Buy Live Grouper | The Fish Collection',
